data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Welcome to your dream home in Marion County! This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom gem offers everything you've been searching for.  Immaculate landscaping enhances the curb appeal, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere right from the curb. As you step inside, you'll find a modern kitchen equipped with brand new appliances, making meal preparation a joy. You can enjoy peace of mind knowing that the roof was replaced in 2021, ensuring protection from the elements for years to come. The 2017 AC system keeps the interior comfortable and efficient. For those who love outdoor living, this property features a screened-in lanai and an open deck, perfect for relaxing or entertaining. There's also a convenient storage shack for all your tools and equipment. Situated on a spacious corner lot at the end of a peaceful cul-de-sac, you'll have ample space and privacy. Plus, the fresh interior and exterior paint give the home a pristine and well-maintained appearance. This home is the perfect blend of comfort and style, offering a truly wonderful living experience. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity! Contact me for more information or to schedule a viewing.
